{"tid":963002,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺倒數好無謂","createTime":"2018-12-31T09:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T23:16:58.000Z","uid":39980,"like":39,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0bee3b464c06619596541f92f15307addee6a9","tid":963002,"uid":39980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"出街倒數新一年真係好撚弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n「十，九&hellip;&hellip;三，二，一，零!!!Happy new year!!!嘩哇丫嗚嘩啦啦嗚&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n成班戇鳩係到鳩叫，叫撚完之後呢? <br />\n班死o靚仔下一句肯定係問「陣間去邊呀?」 <br />\n然後就會有人答佢「唔知呀，睇你地啦。你地想去邊?」 <br />\n一直Loop&hellip;&hellip;Loop撚到兩三點之後咪返屋企囉 <br />\n<br />\n港奴就唔洗講啦 <br />\n倒數完拿拿林返屋企訓啦，聽日唔洗返工呀!? <br />\n<br />\n咁班MK仔又死去左邊? <br />\n數撚完即刻攬撚住條女開房啪啪啪啦 <br />\n啲MK妹每逢大時大節都同平時一樣架，特別有feel架 <br />\n今晚啪撚到你噴屎呀 <br />\n屌&hellip;其實佢地平時呢個時間咪又係啪緊MK妹 <br />\n洗唔洗特登出黎催情呀? <br />\n<br />\n屌!仲有乜撚野一齊迎接新一年喎 <br />\n不如日日倒數新一日丫，數撚埋新一秒丫柒頭皮 <br />\nHAPPY NEW SECOND呀!!! <br />\n成班智障係到叫叫叫，返屋企訓教啦屌"},{"pid":"e46aa54a4fd382e0e2d9cfebddd928889855d284","tid":963002,"uid":38904,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利  毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21690e18d96cfcb4cee20ad762bb810b67e9a4b","tid":963002,"uid":39980,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"平時番工搭車已經好撚迫 <br />\n倒完數仲更加迫 <br />\n真係打死我都唔撚出去迫"},{"pid":"5990ec00f7596d966b94a5ea459a2d6b14d664da","tid":963002,"uid":39980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"